channel.title: Eklipse ReSpawn
channel.description:
[center][size=24pt]Eklipse ReSpawn[/size][/center]
-[u][b]This Source will only be released on Moparscape, and no where else - if I find it on any other website posted by anyone besides me I'll have it deleted in a minutes notice. [/b][/u]
To kick things off here are the [u][b]Credits[/b][/u] where credits are due. -Delta -Marcbob -Acorn_
Before you download you should know I left out a piece of code having to do with killStreak code, you can find the missing code above the login message. (Without this code it was cause your player to null somewhat.. you'll see..) [b][u]Download links - Credits to Marcbob's 100% compatible Client.[/u][/b] [url=http://uppit.com/9i9gkuask5gd/Eklipse.rar]Server Download[/url] [url=http://uppit.com/9sqchrtzbsd0/2Speced_Client_1.0.rar]Client Download[/url]
[b][u]Server Information[/u][/b]
[u][b]Home Location[/b][/u] Castle Wars lobby - Zamorak portal takes you to edgeville and the Saradomin Portal takes you to the Player's Market.
[u][b]Combat[/b][/u] PvP Combat System - Much more accurate and precise then most other Delta Servers out. PvM Combat System - Hit formulas are very precise but timers are somewhat delayed.
[u][b]Skilling[/b][/u] Skilling isn't much of a main factor in the sever as PvP but its still implented into the game with all skills working, Their not all 100% like other servers claim to have but there basic for what you need to make cash and have fun.
[u][b]Customs[/b][/u] Customs ; A few custom items such as PvP Armour, Dragon Claws, Skillcapes, Avas Accumulator, Void, and the Armadyl Godsword are existing in the servers item database and are implented and working how there supposed to in current day Runescape but are not dropped by any monsters except for the Avas Accumulator and Void knight which can be gained through Pest Control so if you'd like to have a custom free server, its not hard to delete them from game.
[u][b]Starter Location & Gear[/b][/u] As I'm not too much of a big fan for the standard spawning at your home and getting destroyed by spamming bots, I like to set the home locations always a bit unique for instance, your starting location is in the Lost & Found random event which is a closed off mapping with no mapping to be clicking around on, you're instructed to click on the home teleport in your magic book and from there on you're all on your own. As for starter gear your left with 10Million GP, A Iron Scimitar, a bow, some arrows, a staff, and some runes.
I'm sure about half of you didn't read anything above and don't care and just want to see the pictures already, well some say a pictures worth a thousand words, I wonder how much a video is worth? [youtube]http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_Zs-HetPnKw&feature=youtu.be[/youtube]
[img]http://i1040.photobucket.com/albums/b401/AcornsTheName1/ff.png[/img] [img]http://img21.imageshack.us/img21/8366/unled1me.png[/img]
Old Source Pictures ( Some features may not apply anymore ) [img]http://img43.imageshack.us/img43/7296/87705348.png[/img] [img]http://img834.imageshack.us/img834/4751/3333lj.png[/img] [img]http://img713.imageshack.us/img713/8593/unledhxa.png[/img]
Player Account Safety Picture (If you log in from a different IP then last time your asked to enter your pin if you have one set.) [img]http://i1040.photobucket.com/albums/b401/AcornsTheName1/Untitled-6.png[/img]
Finally, I think I've gotten everything in that needs to be said and or shown although most of this post is copy and paste text from my older thread.
